  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Tutoring program for 15 hard of hearing students</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This program is aimed at providing after-school academic tutoring to 15 hard-of-hearing students who attend ordinary school at the age of 7-15 years old . Special education teachers teach them Mandarin Chinese and Mathematics with methods like writing, Q&amp;A, and practice with repetitions that help and enhance hard-of hearing students&apos; understanding.  There will be a social worker who is responsible for case management , and  will teach them social skill and emotional behavior management.</narrative>
  </description>
